comment.body:
@BlazDT 
For Mobile Placeholder in Screenshot 4 and 5, it's not fixed in AdGuard for Windows and AdGuard for Android. It only works for Extension and AG for iOS.
Something like ```sport.de##body > div > .MoltenBundle``` and ```sport.de##body > div > div > div > .MoltenBundle``` do work (AGfW).

